title: When the Water Breaks | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: When the Water Breaks | Joel Osteen
description:
Trials are a sign that you're about to give birth to something new. The process may be uncomfortable, but the end result will be worth it. You're about to give birth to new dreams and unprecedented favor.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
